ge-134523"></figure>



<p></p>



<p>The tangent line is always perpendicular to the radius at that point. To=
 find the equation of the tangent to a circle at a given point, </p>



<p></p>



<ol class=3D"wp-block-list">
<li>Find the gradient of the radius at that point.</li>



<li>Find the gradient of the tangent at that point.</li>



